             was indicted for <rs id="t18220109-62-off310" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220109-62-off310" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220109-62-off310" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220109-62-victim631" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Bass
                        <interp inst="t18220109-62-victim631" type="surname" value="Bass"></interp>
