                  , about six o'clock at night, on the <rs id="t18220109-62-cd311" type="crimeDate">6th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220109-62-off310 t18220109-62-cd311"></join>, and stealing therein, one coat, value 30 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220109-62-victim633" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Lomas
                        <interp inst="t18220109-62-victim633" type="surname" value="Lomas"></interp>
